Version 2.4.60

- make.mak: Added makefile to compile under Cygwin on Windows.
- Makefile: Change to work under Cygwin on Windows and Mac OS X.
- make.mak: File removed.
- stream_t.java (writeFromInputStream()): Added function to write the internal
  buffer directly from the provided InputStream.
- stream_t.java (readIntoOutputStream()): Added to read the internal buffer
  writint to the provided OutputStream.
- socket_t.java (send(stream_t, int)): Changed to use the new function of
  stream_t::readIntoOutputStream(), avoiding temporary memory allocation.
- socket_t.java (read(stream_t, int)): Changed to use the new function
  stream_t::writeFromInputStream() to avoid temporary memory allocation.
